Subject to Subsection (2), funding of disaster relief operations shall be in accordance with the following:•
* the first K15,000.00 shall be borne by the Provincial Government concerned;
* any excess over K15,000.00 and up to K100,000.00 shall be borne equally between the National Government and the Provincial Government concerned;
* any excess over K100,000.00 shall be borne by the National Government.
